	<td><span class="topic">Did any games use background tiles for &quot;sprites&quot;?</span><br /><span class="gensmall"><a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=10807">http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=10807</a></span></td>
