		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I remember an old game console (can't remember which one; might've been a home computer too) where sprites changed color when they crossed into some background areas. I wonder if it was doing software sprites along with a lower-resolution grid for some of the palette bits like on the NES...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


