		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I remember finding one NES game, some vaguely action-adventurey thing, where the boss battles did this—they'd fade out the background, and scroll the boss around while using sprites for the player and everything else.<br /><br />Unfortunately, I can't remember which game this was.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


